This command allows you to sneak up on your target and
suprise them with a stab in the back.  This command can be
used on monsters and players. This is a very powerful skill
and can only be used when you have suprise. The real strength
of this skill is attacking in numbers.  When 'jumping' a
target, after the first stab, other thieves will have
10 seconds in which they may also stab.  After that time,
the target will be too 'aware' of its surroundings to be
taken by anyone else. You *must* be Hidden to stab a fellow
player.

This skill is based on your Dex & Int, as well as your Glevel.
It is a Glevel 11 skill.

Syntax: stab <target>
